RAINE v. AMERICAN STEEL & WIRE CO. OF NEW JERSEY. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. January 29, 1903.) No. 79. In Error to the Circuit Court of the United States for the Northern District of New York. F. E. Smith, for plaintiff in error. C. C. Van Kirk, for defendant In error.

Before WALLACE and LACOMBB, Circuit Judges.

No opinion. Affirmed in open court.
